  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive piece of self-adhesive, crease-proof wall art.<br><br>Is your home planet overburdened with industrial waste? Troubled by crates and barrels exploding in the night? Looking to earn rewards for responsible disposal? Purchase a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Gravitino Coil</span> today!",
